\lang english
Compliance with this policy is mandatory for all County personnel and authorized non-employees who are granted logical access to County information technology resources,
 who process or handle County data,
 or who possess unescorted physical access to areas designated as physically secure locations.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
\lang english
Assessment
